;(First interaction)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 801415091: Config/Level/Mission/8014150/Act/Act801415091.json-->
::'''Barrie:''' Oh, you're an Aetherium Wars player?
::'''Barrie:''' Uhh... Well you see, I'm the Interastral Tournament Festival operator, I distribute player benefits here.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Player benefits?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_814111604-->
:::'''Barrie:''' That's right, the IPC asked me to work this stall and hand out gifts to players to promote Aetherium Wars, and encourage players to come to the festival in person.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'm a player, give me benefits.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_814111606-->
:::'''Barrie:''' Hold on, you still don't know how this works, do you? They are benefits, but there are conditions that have to be met to claim them.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_814111607-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_814111607-->
::'''Barrie:''' When you complete the Victory Zone trials and defeat a Championship Contender, you will receive Mastery Marks that you can use to claim benefits here.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What benefits are there?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_814111609-->
:::'''Barrie:''' What benefits are there... Hmm, what are they? Let me see...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} They must be pretty generous, right?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_814111611-->
:::'''Barrie:''' Don't get your hopes up too high! The IPC is stingy with their employees, I can only imagine how they are with players. Let me see...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} It's not just a load of trash, right?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_814111613-->
:::'''Barrie:''' I wouldn't think so? They've put so much effort into holding a festival, the benefits can't be that bad. Let me see...
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_814111614-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_814111614-->
::'''Barrie:''' No way, they're actually pretty good! There are powerful {{Color|keyword|nobold=1|Aether Expansion Chips}}, as well as limited-edition {{Color|keyword|nobold=1|Aether Spirits}}!
::'''Barrie:''' I guess that makes sense, there won't be many people that can defeat Championship Contenders, after all... Anyway, if you manage to get yourself some Mastery Marks, come to me for your benefits.
;(Subsequent interactions)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 801415092: Config/Level/Mission/8014150/Act/Act801415092.json-->
::'''Barrie:''' Oh, it's you! Are you here to claim benefits?
