::<!--Custom String Trigger: Talk_801415094-->
:{{DIcon}} I want to chat with you...
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 801415095: Config/Level/Mission/8014150/Act/Act801415095.json-->
::'''Barrie:''' Alright, this job is pretty dull, let's chat.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Do you enjoy your job?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_814111803-->
:::'''Barrie:''' Do I seem like I am enjoying myself? This is clearly something the devs could make a system for, yet they have me standing here for days on end!
:::'''Barrie:''' I spend all day wasting my time explaining player benefits, and I never get to give any out. Do the higher-ups really think that many people will beat Championship Contenders? Does senior management not look at player stats?
:::'''Barrie:''' Ah, I won't be doing this job again...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Do you like Aetherium Wars?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_814111807-->
:::'''Barrie:''' Aetherium Wars...? I used to like it a lot, why else would I come to work here? But now I've lost all interest.
:::'''Barrie:''' It used to be that playing Aetherium Wars after work was my one joy in life. But since I started working for them and exhausting myself here every day, just hearing the name makes my jaw clench.
:::'''Barrie:''' But what can I do? A hobby always gets boring when it becomes a job.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Let's talk about Wilder.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_814111811-->
:::'''Barrie:''' Wilder? What's there to talk about, what a buzz kill!
:::'''Barrie:''' Ever since he became head of operations at the "Interastral Tournament Festival," he's arranged overtime every day, set up after-work meetings and started calling in the middle of the night to discuss plans! We employees can't even get a good sleep!
:::'''Barrie:''' He is dedicated to his work and clearly loves it, but most people are just working to get food on the table! Who wants to work themselves into the ground every day for his dreams!?
:::'''Barrie:''' Ahem, please don't report this back to him. If I get fired, there will be no one here to give you benefits.
::{{DIcon|Exit}} That's all I wanted to talk about.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_814111816-->
:::'''Barrie:''' Alright, let me get back to my hard labor. Good luck!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
